# 16. Limitations

Although the prototype successfully demonstrates AI customer support automation, several limitations remain.

## JSON-Based Storage

The prototype currently uses JSON files instead of a production-grade database.



## Limited Product Catalog

Only sample product and order data are available.



## No Authentication

The chatbot does not currently support user login or authorization mechanisms.



## No Persistent Chat History

Customer conversations are not stored for future reference.



## No Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)

The system relies on prompt-based generation and does not retrieve information from external knowledge bases.



